1188
01:24:49,700 --> 01:24:50,800
Không! Ahh...

1189
01:24:59,540 --> 01:25:00,540
Không!

1190
01:25:02,630 --> 01:25:03,630
Không!

1191
01:25:11,800 --> 01:25:13,110
Hiccup!

1192
